This paper discusses the need for and implementation of subset query processing in relational databases, which falls under the category of database systems (cs.DB). The paper also introduces new operators and constructs for expressing subset queries, which could be considered a data structure (cs.DS) or language (cs.LG) topic. The examples provided in the paper demonstrate the potential applications of subset queries, which could be relevant to information retrieval (cs.IR) or artificial intelligence (cs.AI) systems.
